ouths of the prophe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> and apo&s;tles, in behalf of his people. Now as the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> were moved to the&s;e prayers, by the in&s;piration and in+fluence of the Holy Gho&s;t, tho&s;e prayers may be re+garded as God's wre&s;tlings for his people.</P>
